name: Open My Heart Valentines Day Card
description: This is a lovely interactive card perfect for your gal or fella! It starts out as a normal looking envelope, sealed with a kiss, and as it is unfolded the envelope opens up into a heart. On the inside it reads "You've opened my heart to love. Happy Valentines Day!" A literal expression of an internal action. Let the ones you love know how much you care with this simple heartfelt card!
